#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:1026(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:1026(para)
msgid ""
"To install <application>PHP5</application> package, please refer to the "
"<xref linkend=\"php5\"/> section."
msgstr ""
"Pour installer le paquet <application>PHP5</application>, veuillez consulter "
"la section <xref linkend=\"php5\"/> de ce guide."

#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:1033(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:1033(para)
