"Vérifions maintenant la modification apportée au fichier de configuration "
"<filename>/etc/lighttpd/lighttpd.conf</filename>. Lancez les commandes "
"suivantes pour arrêter et vérifier la modication :"

#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:1050(programlisting) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:1050(programlisting)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"sudo /etc/init.d/lighttpd stop\n"
"sudo lighttpd -f /etc/lighttpd/lighttpd.conf\n"
msgstr ""
"\n"
"sudo /etc/init.d/lighttpd stop\n"
"sudo lighttpd -f /etc/lighttpd/lighttpd.conf\n"

#: ../generic/server/C/web-servers.xml:1054(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/web-servers.xml:1054(para)
msgid ""
"If you see any errors, please make sure to address them. The error message "
