#: ../generic/server/C/network-applications.xml:1183(para) ../generic/server/C/file-server.xml:312(para) ../generic/serverguide/C/file-server.xml:312(para)
msgid ""
"<emphasis role=\"bold\">ServerAdmin</emphasis>: To configure the email "
